source.name: Patent Application Publication Single-Page TIFF Images (October 2010 - Present)
source.description: Contains the images of each patent application publication (non-provisional utility and plant) published weekly (Thursdays) from October 7, 2010 to present in Tagged Image File Format (TIFF) Revision 6.0 with CCITT Group 4 Compression (single-page TIFFs) from the USPTO Patent Application Image/TIFF (aka Yellow Book 2) product. Files include: app_yb2_yyyymmdd.tar [where "yyyymmdd" is a Thursday publication date].
